{"id":157326,"type":1,"name":"八犬伝","summary":"安房国・里見家の伏姫は、戦で手柄を立てた飼い犬・八房と結婚し、やがて懐妊。 犬の子を身ごもった身を嘆き、命を絶つ。その瞬間、姫の数珠から、八つの珠が飛び散った。 その珠と牡丹の痣を持つ八人の青年がこの物語の主人公…八犬士たちである。 やがて八犬伝は、彼らの青春へと舞台を移していく…","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>八犬传</li><li><span>册数: </span>15</li><li><span>作画: </span><a href=\"/person/20490\">碧也ぴんく</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/11407\">曲亭馬琴</a>『南総里見八犬伝』</li><li><span>出版社: </span>角川書店</li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>コミックGENKi</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1991-04</li><li><span>开始: </span>1989年2月</li><li><span>结束: </span>2005年5月</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"staff":[{"id":20490,"image":"","name":"碧也绯红","desc":"作画"},{"id":11407,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/88/47/11407_prsn_06L0t.jpg","name":"曲亭马琴","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":157346,"image":"","title":"BLIND GAME","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/157346"},{"id":157335,"image":"","title":"八犬伝 文庫版","type":"不同版本","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/157335"}],"comic":[{"id":157324,"name":"八犬伝 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/2c/157324_jp.jpg"},{"id":157325,"name":"八犬伝 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/45/06/157325_jp.jpg"},{"id":157323,"name":"八犬伝 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/98/c8/157323_jp.jpg"},{"id":157322,"name":"八犬伝 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/8b/43/157322_jp.jpg"},{"id":157321,"name":"八犬伝 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1b/22/157321_jp.jpg"},{"id":157320,"name":"八犬伝 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9c/68/157320_jp.jpg"},{"id":157319,"name":"八犬伝 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ac/8c/157319_jp.jpg"},{"id":157315,"name":"八犬伝 (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6d/86/157315_jp.jpg"},{"id":157313,"name":"八犬伝 (9)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/25/9c/157313_jp.jpg"},{"id":157318,"name":"八犬伝 (10)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/0f/31/157318_jp.jpg"},{"id":157317,"name":"八犬伝 (11)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e8/03/157317_jp.jpg"},{"id":157316,"name":"八犬伝 (12)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b1/50/1